{"tid":1969232,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"全港最大騎劫行動","createTime":"2020-04-12T09:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T07:51:10.000Z","uid":273593,"like":115,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"d62586f9b1114e4e9ae2160060004498289d3800","tid":1969232,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:26:38.000Z","msg":"連燈仔拍手、演唱會要人！！！<br />\n<br />\nwiki: <em><ins>1989羅馬尼亞革命</ins></em><br />\n共產黨總書記在集會上講話，近十萬人被動員參加。現場出現喇叭大聲聲稱，保安部隊正向人群射擊，一場<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span></strong></span>已經開始。<br />\n<br />\n結果及結論:<br />\n羅馬尼亞人參加政府造勢大會，最後引致共產政權被推翻，進行民主化改革。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">政府造勢大會，不等於要杯葛。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">相反，只要有心抗爭，應該要利用每一個場合，爭取曝光率，同埋凝聚士氣，叫出光復香港嘅口號。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n獨裁政權最喜歡人們互相不信任、互相分化。 因為人們嘅集結，就係對佢哋造成最大嘅危險。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋最強大係騎劫，譬如高嗌支持醫護嘅口號 ，但做相反嘅事情。<br />\n<br />\n如果我係林鄭，我會搵曬全部人合作，杯葛所謂嘅黃絲。<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係所謂「歸邊理論」。 獨裁政權利用權力同金錢，逼使大部分人同佢合作。<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，唔好害怕參與政府舉辦嘅活動、支持嘅集會。那怕係拍掌活動，或者係許冠傑演唱會，雖然獲得政權加持。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">參與呢啲活動，反而成為咗合法嘅抗辯，沒有人能夠擔保，有一天我地可能像羅馬尼亞。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n廣東話有一句<ins>「食碗麵反碗底」</ins>，活學活用。<br />\n<br />\n再講一次，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">能夠聚集士氣、人群嘅地方，就應該有手足嘅影子，做到真正be water。不反對通知書只係一個形式去集結，同樣道理，政府支持嘅活動一樣可以滲透。</span><br />\n<br />\n到政府每一次活動都有市民去「支持」，風聲鶴唳嘅日子，就係我哋勝利嘅一天。"},{"pid":"f2790d0576ab288ce9edc10e37d7362d8d321350","tid":1969232,"uid":273593,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:28:42.000Z","msg":"有人會反駁係咪要加入共產黨活動<br />\n<br />\n如果有一日共產黨舉行集會<br />\n<br />\n大家就去大嗌口號逼佢放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n羅馬尼亞革命成功，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為全國直播都見到啲人大嗌要革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b97b795515427be9dc0d6556af2046c41726ed75","tid":1969232,"uid":273593,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"結論:<br />\n<br />\n獨裁政權最鍾意騎劫每一個群組，<br />\n<br />\n我哋反其道而行，<br />\n<br />\n大家永遠都要記得一個結論，<br />\n<br />\n政府支持醫護行動，<br />\n<br />\n我哋就大嗌康復香港時代抗疫。<br />\n<br />\nBe water"},{"pid":"2a2d130ed0bf253504ac0501883ec2003a35f83c","tid":1969232,"uid":273593,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:31:28.000Z","msg":"大家集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n可以點樣騎劫政府嘅文宣活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2671c88868e46dc7a4ece81c428852bc251369e9","tid":1969232,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"推行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e58c9ac994fc4c0ed6a7d680d4e561720d70bc","tid":1969232,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"樓主p牌,入黎推po嘅又係p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n非p巴打你地係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c20afd46682a99a30cfc2e06ee4866b3bc874ba","tid":1969232,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e58c9ac994fc4c0ed6a7d680d4e561720d70bc","tid":1969232,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"樓主p牌,入黎推po嘅又係p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n非p巴打你地係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"心傷 求非P入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\